dismissalText.commentary: Brian Lara st Dhoni b Tendulkar 31 (23b 2x4 2x6 28m) SR: 134.78

dismissalComment.html: Tendulkar ends Lara's knock. Anticipating that Lara would come down the track, he fires is a seam-up delivery, full and outside off stump, Lara is beaten by the pace and the length as he tries to stab at it and Dhoni pulls off a smart stumping. That is a huge wicket and tilts the scale back towards India.

dismissalText.commentary: Brian Lara st Dhoni b Tendulkar 31 (23b 2x4 2x6 28m) SR: 134.78

dismissalComment.html: Tendulkar ends Lara's knock. Anticipating that Lara would come down the track, he fires is a seam-up delivery, full and outside off stump, Lara is beaten by the pace and the length as he tries to stab at it and Dhoni pulls off a smart stumping. That is a huge wicket and tilts the scale back towards India.
